- Indeed! Then, who is he?

1605
02:02:22,512 --> 02:02:24,095
I'll find out.

1606
02:02:24,305 --> 02:02:27,630
Hey! Who are you?
- Who are you?

1607
02:02:27,720 --> 02:02:29,888
I am Hrishikesh Chatterjee!

1608
02:02:30,138 --> 02:02:32,055
I am Bomkesh Chatterjee!

1609
02:02:32,180 --> 02:02:35,055
This girl is going to be my wife!

1610
02:02:35,512 --> 02:02:37,845
I have already
become the girl's husband!

1611
02:02:37,970 --> 02:02:40,553
She is going to be my wife!

1612
02:02:40,888 --> 02:02:42,553
